I'm a bit confused on why the xyz.openbmc_project.Dump.Manager InterfacesAdded d-bus event from PDC would have "InProgress". Doesn't the code you have here actually start the dump (i.e. updateProgressStatus())?

The idea is for the dump entries to be created with InProgress status in PDC, and this monitor app will pick such entries and collect the dump.
if dump collection fails, this service will update the status as failed.
if not, the packaged file will be loaded in the dump storage space, which will be picked up by PDC and fill in other details like size and status as completed.
Acknowledged
